Edgar M. Purvis Jr.COO & Executive VP, Emerson Electric Co.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 2 Board Members in 2 different organizations across 3 different industries.See Board Relationships60$4,419,127As of Fiscal Year 2016
Background

		Mr. Edgar M. Purvis, Jr. also known as Ed, has been the Chief Operating Officer at Emerson Electric Co. since January 2015. Mr. Purvis serves as an Executive Vice President of Emerson Electric Co. He served as an Executive Vice President of Emerson and Business Leader for Emerson Climate Technologies, Inc. since May 2008 until January 2015. He served as a Vice President of The Air-Conditioning, Heating and Refrigeration Institute. He served as an Executive Vice President ... of Emerson and Business Leader for Emerson Climate Technologies, Inc.  since May 2008. He served as Vice President of Emerson Climate Technologies, Inc. until May 2008. He joined Emerson in 1983 as Product Planner with Copeland and he assumed a number of Senior Management positions in air conditioning Marketing, Sales and Product Planning and served as a Vice President of Marketing since 1993. He served as Vice President of Sales and Marketing at Emerson since 1995 and also served as its President of Refrigeration from 1996 to 2003 and Vice President of Refrigeration since 2003. He serves as a Director of Premier Health Partners, Inc. He serves as a Director of The Air-Conditioning, Heating and Refrigeration Institute. He is a Member of Dayton President Club, University of Dayton's Executive Development Program and is actively involved in Troy Christian School. Mr. Purvis holds Bachelor's degree in Mechanical Engineering from the University of Tennessee, Master's Degree in Mechanical Engineering from the University of Michigan and Master of Business Administration from Capital University in Columbus, Ohio.Read Full Background




