Edgar M. Purvis Jr., MBA

Age : 59Public asset : 10,117,335 USDLinked companies :  Emerson Electric Co. 





Summary 



Mr. Edgar M. Purvis is Chief Operating Officer at Emerson Electric Co. and President at Copeland Corp. LLC.He is on the Board of Directors at Air-Conditioning Heating & Refrigeration Institute, North American Technician Excellence, Inc., Premier Health Partners, Inc. and Victoria Theatre Association. Mr. Purvis was previously employed as Executive Vice President by Emerson Climate Technologies.He also served on the board at Dayton Development Coalition, Inc.He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Tennessee, a graduate degree from the University of Michigan and an MBA from Capital University.



